OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779624669
OL,3,CRape victim says decision to spare her
OL,4,Cattackers jail was like 'rock in my
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FA judge's decision not to jail two
OL,8,Fteenage boys who raped two girls has
OL,9,Fbeen described by one of the victims
OL,10,Fas a "rock straight in my face".
OL,12,FThe trial at Southampton Crown Court
OL,13,Fheard the girls were raped in two
OL,14,Fseparate incidents in Fordingbridge,
OL,15,FHampshire, the first attack on
OL,16,FNovember 26 2024 and the second on
OL,17,FJanuary 17 2025.
OL,26,@rD@FOUrD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
