FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779624669
OL,3,CRape victim says decision to spare her
OL,4,Cattackers jail was like 'rock in my
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FThe boys, both aged 15, were given
OL,8,Fyouth rehabilitation orders (YRO) and
OL,9,Fmade subject to intensive supervision
OL,10,Fand surveillance (ISS).
OL,12,FIn an interview with the BBC's Sunday
OL,13,FWith Laura Kuenssberg programme, one
OL,14,Fof the victims, who was 15 at the time
OL,15,Fof the incident, said of the boys'
OL,16,Fsentence: "The words hit like a rock
OL,17,Fstraight in my face.
OL,26,@xD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779624669
OL,3,CRape victim says decision to spare her
OL,4,Cattackers jail was like 'rock in my
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,F"He (the judge) almost made it seem as
OL,8,Fif what the boys did was not OK, but
OL,9,Fit was OK in the eyes of the law,
OL,10,Fbecause they were still children."
OL,12,FSpeaking anonymously alongside her
OL,13,Ffamily, the now-16-year-old asked:
OL,14,F"What was the point in putting me
OL,15,Fthrough that?"
OL,17,FJodie Mittel KC, prosecuting, told the
OL,18,Ftrial the girl had visited one of the
OL,19,Fdefendants in November 2024 after
OL,20,Fmeeting him on Snapchat.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@bO]vD@AOUwD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
