PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779624669
OL,3,CRape victim says decision to spare her
OL,4,Cattackers jail was like 'rock in my
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FThe prosecutor said that after
OL,8,Fperforming sex acts on the boy, who
OL,9,Fwas then 14, she became "scared and
OL,10,Fanxious" when the second defendant
OL,11,Farrived, and the pair raped her while
OL,12,Fthe incident was filmed.
OL,14,FMs Mittel said that afterwards, videos
OL,15,Fof the incident had been sent around
OL,16,Fand other people made jokes about her,
OL,17,Fand she received messages calling her
OL,18,Fa "slag".
OL,26,@qD@YOUrD@HO]zD@COUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779624669
OL,3,CRape victim says decision to spare her
OL,4,Cattackers jail was like 'rock in my
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FThe girl told the BBC that she "wanted
OL,8,Fto die" when she received such
OL,9,Fmessages.
OL,11,FThe complainant in the January
OL,12,Fincident, who was 14 at the time, was
OL,13,Fraped in a field near to Fordingbridge
OL,14,Frecreation ground while the incident
OL,15,Fwas also filmed.
OL,17,FIn the sentencing hearing on Thursday,
OL,18,Fa 15-year-old boy was handed a three-
OL,19,Fyear YRO with 180 days of ISS for the
OL,20,Frape of each of the two girls and two
OL,21,Findecent images charges.
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779624669
OL,3,CRape victim says decision to spare her
OL,4,Cattackers jail was like 'rock in my
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FThe court heard he had been diagnosed
OL,8,Fwith ADHD as well as "long-standing
OL,9,Fanxiety".
OL,11,FA second 15-year-old was given the
OL,12,Fsame sentence for three charges of
OL,13,Frape against each of the two victims
OL,14,Fand four counts of taking indecent
OL,15,Fimages in relation to filming of the
OL,16,Fincidents.
OL,18,FThe court was told he had an IQ of the
OL,19,F"bottom 1% of his contemporaries" and
OL,20,Fhad been diagnosed with ADHD.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@HO]{D@AOU{D@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
