OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779624669
OL,3,CRape victim says decision to spare her
OL,4,Cattackers jail was like 'rock in my
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FA third boy, 14, was given a YRO for
OL,8,F18 months for two charges of rape in
OL,9,Fthe January incident by encouraging
OL,10,Fthe second defendant and an offence of
OL,11,Findecent images.
OL,13,FHe was described as having "mild
OL,14,Fcognitive impairment".
OL,16,FJudge Nicholas Rowland told the
OL,17,Fdefendants: "I have to remember that
OL,18,Fyou are not small adults.
OL,26,@uD@\OUvD@UO]yD@MOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779624669
OL,3,CRape victim says decision to spare her
OL,4,Cattackers jail was like 'rock in my
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,F"I have to think how likely you are to
OL,8,Fdo serious things again and I need to
OL,9,Fmake sure you do not do serious things
OL,10,Fagain in the future."
OL,12,FExplaining his sentence, he said: "I
OL,13,Fshould avoid criminalising these
OL,14,Fchildren unnecessarily and understand
OL,15,Fthe effects of their behaviour and
OL,16,Fsupport their reintegration into
OL,17,Fsociety."
OL,19,FHe added that "peer pressure played a
OL,20,Flarge part in what went on".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@UO]tD@cOUyD@IO]{D@OOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779624669
OL,3,CRape victim says decision to spare her
OL,4,Cattackers jail was like 'rock in my
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FThe girl's mother said the case "needs
OL,8,Fto be reviewed".
OL,10,F"This needs to be reviewed, this needs
OL,11,Fto be relooked at, this needs to be
OL,12,Fgiven justice, this needs to be given
OL,13,Fa custodial sentence," the mother told
OL,14,Fthe BBC.
OL,26,@oD@aOUpD@OO]rD@AOUuD@VO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779624669
OL,3,CRape victim says decision to spare her
OL,4,Cattackers jail was like 'rock in my
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,F"That's it. Has to be. We need to
OL,8,Fremember this was not a couple of
OL,9,Fdrunken teenagers at a party having a
OL,10,Ffumble. This was premeditated, it was
OL,11,Fthought about, it was planned, and
OL,12,Fit's not just a one-off occasion. This
OL,13,Fis more than once, this is twice.
OL,15,F"They've been convicted twice of the
OL,16,Fsame thing. How are they still walking
OL,17,Faround?"
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779624669
OL,3,CRape victim says decision to spare her
OL,4,Cattackers jail was like 'rock in my
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FShe also issued an appeal to Prime
OL,8,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer, asking: "If
OL,9,Fit was your daughter, your niece, your
OL,10,Fson, your nephew, your family member,
OL,11,Fwould you be happy?
OL,13,F"Because we're not happy and I don't
OL,14,Fthink any other member of the public
OL,15,Fwill be happy too. So you're in a
OL,16,Fposition of power to help, so please
OL,17,Fhelp."
OL,26,@pD@dOUuD@AOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779624669
OL,3,CRape victim says decision to spare her
OL,4,Cattackers jail was like 'rock in my
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FChief Secretary to the Prime Minister
OL,8,FDarren Jones told the BBC's Sunday
OL,9,FWith Laura Kuenssberg: "Those girls
OL,10,Fdeserve justice, as do their families,
OL,11,Fboth for them, but also for other
OL,12,Fgirls that are put in that position.
OL,14,F"And quite frankly, other boys need to
OL,15,Fknow that they can't behave in that
OL,16,Fway and get away with it."
OL,26,@qD@XOUvD@AOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779624669
OL,3,CRape victim says decision to spare her
OL,4,Cattackers jail was like 'rock in my
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FHe suggested the case would be
OL,8,Freviewed quickly, and said: "We all
OL,9,Fwant to look at this urgently, and the
OL,10,FAttorney General's made that
OL,11,Fcommitment."
OL,13,FSpeaking to BBC Breakfast on Sunday,
OL,14,FHampshire police and crime
OL,15,Fcommissioner Donna Jones said: "What
OL,16,Fis really alarming is the judge's
OL,17,Fcomments praising these three young
OL,18,Fmales for their good conduct from the
OL,19,Fcharge up to the point of their
OL,20,Fsentence.
OL,26,@pD@]OUsD@LO]wD@`OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779624669
OL,3,CRape victim says decision to spare her
OL,4,Cattackers jail was like 'rock in my
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,F"But let's not forget, these were not
OL,8,Fguilty pleas that were entered.
OL,10,F"This is three males who put their
OL,11,Fvictims through the trial and the
OL,12,Fordeal of having to re-live all of
OL,13,Fthat. That has really added to the
OL,14,Fburden for those two survivors."
OL,16,FMs Jones said she agrees that
OL,17,Frehabilitation is "important", but
OL,18,Fadded: "These are not low-level
OL,19,Foffences. They are some of the worst
OL,20,Foffences you can do to another human
OL,21,Fbeing.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUvD@`O]yD@SOUyD@]O]zD@HOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779624669
OL,3,CRape victim says decision to spare her
OL,4,Cattackers jail was like 'rock in my
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,F"The police often refer to rape as the
OL,8,Fworst offence you can survive... and
OL,9,Fthe victims will have to live with the
OL,10,Fconsequences of this for the rest of
OL,11,Ftheir lives.
OL,13,F"That's why (a custodial sentence) is
OL,14,Fappropriate, for the protection of
OL,15,Fothers and so (the culprits) can get
OL,16,Fthat support in prison. They should be
OL,17,Fsent to youth offending."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
