CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779624669
OL,3,CRape victim says decision to spare her
OL,4,Cattackers jail was like 'rock in my
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FA Government spokesman said the
OL,8,Fattorney general's office had received
OL,9,F"multiple" requests for the sentences
OL,10,Fto be reviewed under the Unduly
OL,11,FLenient Scheme.
OL,13,FHe said: "We share the public's shock
OL,14,Fat the details of this horrific case,
OL,15,Fand our thoughts are with the young
OL,16,Fvictims during this distressing time.
OL,18,F"The law officers are urgently
OL,19,Freviewing the case with the utmost
OL,20,Fcare and attention."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@JO]uD@JOUzD@AOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G16/17
